        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="《孤独》"><a href="#《孤独》" class="headerlink" title="《孤独》"></a>《孤独》</h2><h3 id="白鹤林"><a href="#白鹤林" class="headerlink" title="白鹤林"></a>白鹤林</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-c++" data-language="c++"><code class="language-c++">从童年起我便独自一人照顾着历代星辰<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>白先生的短诗《孤独》，初读时便有深深共鸣。</p><hr><p><small>（最后修订日期：2021-06-30）</small></p>]]></content>
      
      
